# --- Generated migration data (personal inventory — never commit) -------------
# Everything under manifests/ is a per-machine inventory produced by /collect +
# /verify (app lists, versions, paths, hardware model, staged plugin/ICC binaries,
# generated install/verify scripts and the migration report) — EXCEPT the tracked
# schema templates. Ignore-by-default guards against accidentally committing
# personal data; only manifests/templates/ is version-controlled.
manifests/*
!manifests/templates/

# --- Local / personal Claude Code config --------------------------------------
# Personal overrides (disabled MCP servers, machine-specific permission allows).
# The shared, recommended permission model is documented in .claude/rules.md §1.
.claude/settings.local.json

# --- macOS / editor noise -----------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
*.swp
